<h3>claw/amrclaw/2d/lib</h3>
<p>
Most routines aren't listed yet....

<dl>
<dt>[code: amr2ez.f]
<dd> The main routine.


<dt>[code: bc2amr.f]
<dd> Imposes boundary conditions by extending values in the computational
grid to ghost cells on either side.

If you want to add a new boundary condition, copy this file to your
application directory, modify it, 
and then modify the Makefile to point to the new version.



</dl>
